    <text>
        
        <front>
            <div type="editorial_desc">
                <p>Political cartoon of Jefferson Davis' inauguration in Richmond, VA, as President of the Confederate States of America. Depicts Davis as a skeleton holding a pirate flag and a torch to "Desolation," guarding a slave between his legs, and perched on a bale of cotton. Drunk men and a starving woman and child are depicted in the background. Features a quote from Davis' inaugural speech as a caption.</p>
            </div>
        </front>

        <body>
            <div type="image_transcription" facs="#HM" n="1">
