                <p>MARCH 15, 1862</p>
            </div>
            
            <div type="image_transcription" facs="#Title" n="3">
                <head><supplied resp="editorial">Title and caption</supplied></head>
                <p>THE INAUGURATION AT RICHMOND.</p>
                <p>"Fellow Citizens!  On this the Birthday of the Man most identified with the Establishment of American Independence and beneath the Monument erected, &amp;c., &amp;c., &amp;c., we have assembled to usher into existence the permanent Government of the Confederate States."â€”(JEFF DAVIS'S <hi rendition="#italics">Inaugural Address at Richmond.)</hi></p>
            </div>
            
            <div type="image_transcription" facs="#Whiskey" n="4">
